#: ../../../source/docs/porting/connecting_cpp_and_javascript/Interacting-with-code.rst:357
msgid ""
"It is possible to implement a C API in JavaScript! This is the approach used "
"in many of Emscripten's libraries, like SDL1 and OpenGL."
